                <div class="center">

                    Recipes posted on this site can come from anyone and anywhere. Some may be intended to be taken seriously, others...not so
                    much.

                    <br />
                    <br /> Use good judgement when browsing our site and, as always, never consume anything harmful to your health:

                </div>

                <br />

                <ul>

                    <li> Nothing toxic</li>
                    <li> Nothing you're allergic to</li>
                    <li> No overindulging in alcohol</li>
                    <li> No underage drinking</li>
                    <li> No drunk driving</li>
                    <li> No drunk spellcasting</li>
                    <li> No consumption of magical substances without a high-level wizard present</li>

                </ul>

                <br />

                <div class="center">

                    Oh, and no wasting years of your life searching for fictional and/or supernatural ingredients...that's not a health warning
